Summary
-------

- Protocols, SDKs, CLI, and framework adapters are licensed under the
  Apache License, Version 2.0. The full text is in LICENSE.apache.

- The runtime, services, and official plugins are licensed under the
  Business Source License 1.1, with a Change Date four years after each
  release at which the license converts to Apache License, Version 2.0.
  The full text is in LICENSE.bsl.

For details, see LICENSING.md in this directory.

For commercial licensing inquiries, contact licensing@objectstack.dev.
